# cPanel / CloudLinux Passenger — Node.js API (api.danielasantos.work)
#
# Upload to ~/api.danielasantos.work/.htaccess (same folder as loader.cjs).
# Verify PassengerNodejs matches cPanel → Setup Node.js App (Node 18 → /18/, Node 20 → /20/).
# Preferred fix if the file is missing: Setup Node.js App → Edit → Save (regenerates this file).

# DO NOT REMOVE. CLOUDLINUX PASSENGER CONFIGURATION BEGIN
PassengerAppRoot "/home/dmolnlpq/api.danielasantos.work"
PassengerBaseURI "/"
PassengerNodejs "/home/dmolnlpq/nodevenv/api.danielasantos.work/20/bin/node"
PassengerAppType node
PassengerStartupFile loader.cjs
# DO NOT REMOVE. CLOUDLINUX PASSENGER CONFIGURATION END
